Changed files (3): src/main/java/io/vertx/core/json/jackson/HybridJacksonPool.java, src/main/java/io/vertx/core/json/jackson/JacksonCodec.java, src/test/java/io/vertx/core/json/jackson/HybridJacksonPoolTest.java
Diff (+352/-1):
PR DESCRIPTION:
This pull request is a follow up of the work done to make the [internal pool used by Jackson configurable and pluggable](https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson-core/pull/1064). It is not intended to be merged until Jackson 2.16 won't be released. Also this is the porting of the [same pull request sent to quarkus](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/35816).

